# Depot Manager Credentials

This document contains the generated credentials for the Tamil Nadu Bus Depot Selection Platform managers. These correspond to the depots seeded in the database.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Privacy Notice**: These credentials should only be visible to the system administrator and the respective depot managers.

| Depot Name | Manager ID (Email) | Default Password |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **MTC - Chennai Central** | `manager.D001@tnstc.gov.in` | `D001_pass123` |
| **TNSTC - Madurai Central** | `manager.D002@tnstc.gov.in` | `D002_pass123` |
| **TNSTC - Coimbatore Town** | `manager.D003@tnstc.gov.in` | `D003_pass123` |
| **SETC - Tirunelveli** | `manager.D004@tnstc.gov.in` | `D004_pass123` |
| **TNSTC - Salem City** | `manager.D005@tnstc.gov.in` | `D005_pass123` |
| **MTC - T. Nagar** | `manager.D006@tnstc.gov.in` | `D006_pass123` |
| **TNSTC - Trichy Central** | `manager.D007@tnstc.gov.in` | `D007_pass123` |
| **... and so on** | `manager.<DEPOT_ID>@tnstc.gov.in` | `<DEPOT_ID>_pass123` |

### Access Instructions
1. Navigate to `/depot-login` (or click "Manager Login" on the main login page).
2. Enter the **Manager ID** and **Default Password**.
3. Upon login, managers will only see "Found" reports and matching "Lost" reports for their **assigned depot**.

> [!NOTE]
> All 35+ seeded depots follow this pattern. The `DEPOT_ID` matches the internal code (e.g., `D001`, `D002`).
